room_title: Escape room "The Lost Cabin" by Escape Oshkosh in Oshkosh
room_address: 146 Algoma Blvd Suite C Oshkosh, WI 54901
room_description: Your great grandfather, William, recently passed away and there are rumors that he left behind a vast fortune. You and your family have searched everywhere, but you recently stumbled upon a deed to a cabin that no one knew he owned. Can you search the cabin and find his fortune before the rest of your family?
